                <note rend="inline" type="source">710.Consultation (2)/263: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Costa Rica</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hornibrook</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1940-07-12T18:00:00-04:00"
                            >July 12, 1940—6 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>64. Your 86, July 11, 11 a.m. If you have not already done so, please give the
                    Foreign Minister a copy of my statement in this regard as quoted in Radio
                    Bulletin No. 164, July 11.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
